$ Oracle Optimal Flexible Architecture (OFA)

Oracle base: something like  → Linux/fhs/u01/app/oracle[`/u01/app/oracle`] (Windows: `c:\app\username`)

Oracle home: Something like → Linux/fhs/u01/app/oracle/product/vv-v-v/dbhome_n[`$ORACLE_BASE/product/12.1.0/dbhome_0`] 

{ Filename suffixes

  Control files: `.ctl`

  Log files: `.log`

  Data files: `.dbf`

}
